com.castinfo.devops.robotest.restassured

Class RestAssuredWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.castinfo.devops.robotest.restassured.RestAssuredWrapper

  • public class RestAssuredWrapper
extends Object
    RestAssured utility wrapper. Creates a object with RequestSpecBuilder and ResponseSpecBuilder RestAssured objects to take profit from his fluent API to do REST API Calls. Feel free to use, extend, improve or implement your own utilities. See com.castinfo.devops.robotest.restassured.RestTest for basic use example.

      • when

        public io.restassured.response.Response when(String url,
                                             io.restassured.http.Method httpMethod)
        Do the Call with the spec request, url and method. Be aware that wrapper can't execute N times this call, but you must control response specs reuse.
        Parameters:
        url - By default only relative path to http://localhost:80 you can specify you wan't.
        httpMethod - The RestAssured supported Method
        Returns:
        The Response Object.
